The Magento Payment Gateway Plugin for Bitcoin [[RPC API|API_reference_(JSON-RPC)]] provides the ability for eCommerce sites running Magento to be able to accept bitcoins for payment.

This open source project was released on June 11, 2011 (1.1).

##External Links

* [Magento-Bitcoin-Payment-Module](http://github.com/jalder/Magento-Bitcoin-Payment-Module) project on GitHub
* [Magento Bitcoin Payment Module](https://github.com/BitPagos/bitpagos-magento) for [BitPagos](https://www.bitpagos.net)
* [Bitcoin/Altcoins Plugin for Magento](https://www.btcmerch.com/help/magento) developed by BTCMerch.

